@startuml seq-wearable-sync
title Wearable Data Sync — Sequence Diagram

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Patient" as User
participant "Mobile App\n(React Native)" as App
participant "HealthKit /\nGoogle Fit SDK" as HealthSDK
participant "Wearable API\n(Oura / Whoop)" as WearableAPI
participant "Normalizer\n(on-device)" as Normalizer
participant "API Gateway\n(.NET YARP)" as Gateway
participant "Monitoring API\n(.NET 9)" as API
participant "Cosmos DB" as Cosmos
participant "Azure\nService Bus" as Bus

User -> App : Opens app / background sync triggers
activate App

App -> HealthSDK : Query new data since last sync
activate HealthSDK
HealthSDK --> App : Raw HR, HRV, SpO2, sleep stages
deactivate HealthSDK

App -> WearableAPI : GET /v1/sleep, /v1/heart-rate
activate WearableAPI
WearableAPI --> App : Raw JSON payloads
deactivate WearableAPI

App -> Normalizer : Normalize & deduplicate
activate Normalizer
Normalizer --> App : List<WearableDataPointDto>
deactivate Normalizer

App -> Gateway : POST /api/monitoring/wearable-sync\n[Bearer token + normalized payload]
activate Gateway
Gateway -> API : Route + validate JWT
activate API

API -> API : MediatR: SyncMonitoringDataHandler
API -> API : Create/update MonitoringSession aggregate
API -> API : EvaluateThresholds() — generate PassiveAlerts

API -> Cosmos : Upsert MonitoringSession
activate Cosmos
Cosmos --> API : 200 OK
deactivate Cosmos

API -> Bus : Publish MonitoringDataReceived event
activate Bus
Bus --> API : Accepted
deactivate Bus

API --> Gateway : 200 OK
deactivate API
Gateway --> App : 200 OK
deactivate Gateway

App --> User : Sync complete indicator
deactivate App

@enduml
